    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone prioritizing utility and value. The exterior shows its age with some clear coat peeling on the roof and a few minor scratches along the passenger side doors. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining and wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car starts and runs well, though it will likely require new tires and a brake service within the next few thousand miles. It is a solid, honest car for someone looking for reliable transportation without the premium price tag of a newer model.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
