      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-loved\u2014perfect for someone looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road. I've kept up with all the maintenance, so it's ready to hit the pavement with a new owner today. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 31500.0,
